Chuk,<br>
<br>
There is No comparison that can be made in EQ and DAoC camping. the way they each do exp is completely different.<br>
<br>
In EQ you can kill the same mobs 24/7 365 and they will always be worth the same amount of exp as when you started. <br>
<br>
In DAoC you start killing a camp of mobs and the exp you get slowly gets smaller and smaller till all the bonus is gone and your just getting baseline exp. This is how DAoC rewards you for moving to other spots.<br>
<br>
